Requirements:

  Each flight needs:
  Flight Number
  Flight Date
  Departure Time 
  Arrival Time
  Departure City
  Destination City
  Number of available seats

  Passenger seat reservation info:
  Passenger ID Number (Drive License #, passport, or id)
  Name
  Seat Number
  Flight Number


Design/Steps:

  Main Menu (Defined in project pdf)

  Assign Seats
  
  Display Seat design chart
